<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 32px; }
  .alert { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Backup Code Used</h1>
    <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
    <div class="alert">A two-factor authentication backup code was used to sign in to your account on {{usedAt}}.</div>
    <p>Remaining backup codes: <strong>{{remainingCodes}}</strong>. Generate new codes if you are running low.</p>
    <div class="footer">If this was not you, secure your account immediately.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
